freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Body shaking, especially in neck and head is very noticable. Has been ongoing since just after vaccine and seems worse at times. Headaches persisting and head pressure.
Insomnia with shakin in my body and lightheadedness. Worse. Started on 5th, 3 days after vax though.

It actually started the 5th with body shaking and lightheadedness, but also have not been able to sleep since about the 10th off and on. Have felt nauseous off and on, headaches off and on, and my body has a tremor or internal vibrating feeling.
Shaky, body tremor since 2.5 days post vaccination. Pressure in head, headaches.
Still shaky, lbody vibrating sensation, lightheaded intermittently, which started the 5th, not quite 3 days after vax.
